{"tid":860714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【OPPA】南韓選手扮盲　亞殘運柔道奪金","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T16:59:38.000Z","uid":20634,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"940a7bc2dbc7f102e7d4a4d2d5341d051ae68ffc","tid":860714,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181012/photo/bkn-20181012165602777-1012_00882_001_01p.jpg?20181012211221\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181012%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181012165602777-1012_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20181012211221&h=5e5f7b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在雅加達舉行的亞洲殘疾人運動會，竟然爆出造假事件，一名自稱視障的南韓選手在柔道賽奪得金牌，其後被爆出兩眼視力根本沒有障礙，還在去年考取駕駛執照，惹起各界熱論。事件已被關注，南韓議員表示需要徹底調查。<br />\n<br />\n據稱奪冠的南韓選手所報名的障礙賽事，規定矯正視力0.02以下，屬於障礙二級的項目，但被記者追查後，發現他去年已考了駕駛執照，曾到首爾醫院進行視力檢查，兩眼視力都是1.0。<br />\n<br />\n南韓議員對此甚為關注，並表示真正殘疾人被褫奪了參賽的機會，這次事件需要對體檢過程及選拔程序進行調查。"},{"pid":"9035883bb2b6f0c29c00d47a783590db1078359e","tid":860714,"uid":122264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IQ4KXYF-ic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3IQ4KXYF-ic&d=Dr3og%2FehezBAl2htW82PDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fdf5950a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IQ4KXYF-ic</a>"},{"pid":"3d71ab6a9d08b637551b72c6ed0efdb097a5901e","tid":860714,"uid":152005,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"個腦有事就真 報錯項目姐"},{"pid":"ca635ccbee879cb4dd037ef87d0f72d8e2057f04","tid":860714,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca90c2243827fc4be1a1d4d27b6fce13a717685","tid":860714,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco